children.subject: I’m in the same position and I have no clue what to do

history.content: I tried to enroll in EECS 16A, but I was told that I do not meet the requirements for the reserved seats. However, I'm not really sure why? I'm a current first-year, undeclared L&S. I thought I would fit the "reserved for College of Letters & Sciences: Freshman Students" (but I think that may be for incoming first-year students), so then I figured I might fit the "reserved for College of Letters & Sciences: Undeclared Sophomore Students" that still seems to have seats. Can I get some help/clarification on why I can't enroll?
history.subject: Question About Reserved Seats
